Package: dualmarker
Type: Package
Title: Dual marker analysis for response and survival
Version: 0.1.0
Author: xiaopeng.ma
Maintainer: The package maintainer <xiaopeng.ma@beigene.coms>
Description: A package for dual marker analysis, for response outcome and survival result, 
  using logistic regression, Cox regression model as well as four-quadrant statistics.
  It contains two major modules, one for statistics and visulization of specific biomarker 
  pair, and another one to find another marker2 to combine with marker1
